
# V1 List Pages Response

## Structure

`V1ListPagesResponse`

## Fields

| Name | Type | Tags | Description | Getter | Setter |
|  --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `items` | [`?(V1Page[])`](/doc/models/v1-page.md) | Optional | - | getItems(): ?array | setItems(?array items): void |
